{
  "title": "如何设置文档锚点？",
  "slug": 965195,
  "body_html": "<div data-type=\"p\"><div id=\"7196gk\" data-type=\"image\" data-display=\"block\" data-align=\"left\" data-src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2018/png/84147/1542073118188-8e965462-ef6c-486d-ad6f-9c1ac9c83609.png\" data-width=\"827\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2018/png/84147/1542073118188-8e965462-ef6c-486d-ad6f-9c1ac9c83609.png\" width=\"827\"/></div></div><div data-type=\"p\"></div><div data-type=\"p\">语雀中文档的锚点是以标题为基本跳转单位，所以如果你想在某个链接上加入当前文档的锚点，首先你得有不同级别的标题。从而在<strong>标题左侧点击图标</strong>拷贝锚点。将其复制到链接输入框，点击发布在阅读页面浏览点击相对应的链接即可完成跳转。</div><div data-type=\"p\"></div><div data-type=\"p\"><div id=\"kxkpwa\" data-type=\"image\" data-display=\"block\" data-align=\"left\" data-src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2018/png/84147/1542073297166-85f2288c-8a81-42cc-a858-1e3b129937cb.png\" data-width=\"827\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2018/png/84147/1542073297166-85f2288c-8a81-42cc-a858-1e3b129937cb.png\" width=\"827\"/></div></div><div data-type=\"p\"></div><div data-type=\"p\">同时你自己定义锚点的名称，和你的文档标题相匹配。</div><div data-type=\"p\"></div><div data-type=\"p\"><div id=\"0gnrqr\" data-type=\"image\" data-display=\"block\" data-align=\"left\" data-src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2018/png/84147/1542073435568-76953df7-5854-4abe-bdf5-b5ec034c050b.png\" data-width=\"635\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2018/png/84147/1542073435568-76953df7-5854-4abe-bdf5-b5ec034c050b.png\" width=\"635\"/></div></div><div data-type=\"p\"></div><div data-type=\"p\"></div><div data-type=\"p\">如果要实现跨文档的锚点，那么只需要将对应的锚点地址写到文档的地址的后面即可。比如</div><div data-type=\"p\"></div><div data-type=\"p\"><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" href=\"https://www.yuque.com/yuque/help/about#p4wywv\" class=\"bi-link\">https://www.yuque.com/yuque/help/about#p4wywv</a> </div><div data-type=\"p\"></div><div data-type=\"p\">这个链接可以跳到 “语雀是什么？”中的 “愿景”，这样的链接也可以直接在阅读页面获取，点击标题浏览器左方的#，这个时候浏览器地址会带着标题所在的锚点地址。</div><div data-type=\"p\"></div><div data-type=\"p\"><div id=\"egeqdd\" data-type=\"image\" data-display=\"block\" data-align=\"left\" data-src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2018/png/84147/1542073697643-ae8d952f-d263-4193-bdcf-7ad389735836.png\" data-width=\"827\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2018/png/84147/1542073697643-ae8d952f-d263-4193-bdcf-7ad389735836.png\" width=\"827\"/></div></div><div data-type=\"p\"></div><div data-type=\"p\"></div><div data-type=\"p\"></div>"
}